\{S_n\}
\{X_n\}
S_n/n \rightarrow 0\ a.e.
S_n/n\rightarrow 0\quad in\ probability
S_{2^n}/2^n\rightarrow 0\quad a.e.
 D_n=\max_{2^n\leq k<2^{n+1}}|S_k-S_{2^n}|\rightarrow 0\quad a.e., 
 \frac{|S_k|}{k}\le \frac{|S_{2^n}|+D_n}{2^n}\rightarrow 0\ a.e. \quad \text{for}\quad 2^n\le k<2^{n+1}. 
 \sum_nP\{D_n>2^n\epsilon\}<\infty. 
